*---------------------------------+----------------------+-------------------------------+
|| Variable                       || Type                || Description                 ||
*---------------------------------+----------------------+-------------------------------+
| <<<inputEncoding>>>             | <<<String>>>         |                               |
*---------------------------------+----------------------+-------------------------------+
| <<<outputEncoding>>>            | <<<String>>>         |                               |
*---------------------------------+----------------------+-------------------------------+
| <<<project>>>                   | {{{/ref/current/maven-core/apidocs/org/apache/maven/project/MavenProject.html}<<<MavenProject>>>}} | The current project. |
